文档场景：上市公司企业年报
{
  "document_background": {
    "page_sections": [
      {
        "source_section": "集團首席執行官兼總裁報告",
        "target_section": "Group Chief Executive and President's Report",
        "content_type": "ceo_report",
        "page_range": [
          12,
          16
        ]
      }
    ],
    "roles": [
      {
        "source": "李源祥",
        "target": "Lee Yuen Cheung",
        "role": "Group Chief Executive and President"
      }
    ],
    "terms": [],
    "style_rules": [
      "Use US$ for U.S. dollar amounts.",
      "Keep listed-company annual report disclosure tone formal and publishable.",
      "Do not change numbers, percentages, years, named entities or financial metric values.",
      "For overview narrative, use full financial metric name plus abbreviation when provided.",
      "For financial review and business metrics narrative, use established abbreviations when provided.",
      "Prefer AIA China / AIA Hong Kong / AIA Macau over loose paraphrases when matched."
    ]
  },
  "current_unit": {
    "page_no": 13,
    "unit_id": "p13_g02",
    "unit_mode": "semantic_group",
    "slot_count": 4,
    "source_text": "自疫情大流行開始以來，本集團的各業務團隊反應迅速，積極協助紓緩對社區的影響，同時確保員工安全。本集\n團為此廣泛採取多項措拖，包括財政支持、提供醫療物資、免費保障覆蓋、獲取醫療保健資源、精簡服務流程和\n加快理賠支付，令我引以為榮。我們一如既往找出每一個可以作出理賠的理由，年內已支付逾160億美元的保險\n給付及理賠，為客戶提供極其重要的財務保障。",
    "current_translation": "Since the onset of the pandemic, the Group's business teams have responded swiftly and actively assisted in mitigating the impact on our communities while ensuring employee safety. The Group has implemented a wide range of measures for this purpose, including financial support, provision of medical supplies, complimentary coverage, access to healthcare resources, streamlined service processes and accelerated claims payments, of which I am proud. We have, as always, identified every possible reason to make a claim payment, and have paid out over US$16 billion in insurance benefits and claims during the year, providing our customers with critically important financial protection."
  },
  "output_format": {
    "translations": [
      {
        "unit_id": "p13_g02",
        "translation": "<更紧凑译文>"
      }
    ]
  }
}

